quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,53,"(Ko waɗi) ɗum, ko tawde Alla wonaali waylowo neema mo O neemini e yimɓe haa ɓe wayla ko woni e wonkiiji maɓɓe. E wonnde pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo Annduɗo"
  8,54,"Wano mboowdi yimɓe Fir'awna e ɓen adinooɓe ɓe. Ɓe fennii Aayeeje Joomi maɓɓe ɗen. Men halkiri ɓe junuubi maɓɓe ɗin, Men yooli yimɓe Fir'awna ɓen. Kala (maɓɓe) laatino tooñooɓe"
  8,55,"Pellet, ko ɓuri bonnde e ko ruugata kon ka Alla, ko ɓen yedduɓe, kamɓe ɓe gomɗintaa"
  8,56,"Ɓen ɓe ahodiɗaa e mu'un refti ɓe firta ahadi maɓɓe ndin e kala laawol, kamɓe ɓe hulataa [Alla]"
  8,57,"Si waawii ɓe ka hare, yagginir (sar) ɓe arooɓe ɓaawo maɓɓe. Belajo'o, ɓe waajitoto"
  8,58,"Ammaa si a hulii e yimɓe janfa, bugita(werla) e maɓɓe (firtugol ahadi ndin) dow fotondiral, tawde pellet, Alla yiɗaa janfotooɓe ɓen"
  8,59,"Wata ɓen yedduɓe sikku ɓe laawki. Pellet, kamɓe ɓe ronknitaa (Lam)"
  8,60,"Resoranee(heblanee) ɓe kala ko hattanɗon e doole e pucci hebilaaɗi, hulɓiniron ɗum ayɓe Alla ɓen e ayɓe mon ɓen, e woɗɓe goo gaanin maɓɓe ɓe onon on anndaabe Alla kañun no anndi ɓe. Kala ko nafkudon e laawol Alla ngol hunnanoyte on, onon on tooñoytaake"
  8,61,"Si ɓe naayanike kisal nagl, naayano ngal (an kadi) fawoɗaa e Alla, pellet, Kanko ko O nanoowo annduɗo"